title: Counter-Strike 1.6 DayZ
description: Counter-Strike 1.6 DayZ is a modification of the original Counter-Strike 1.6 game . This client game comes with the latest Steam RIP files . You can play as a Steam Player ! You can play on Steam and No-Steam server ! 100% Clean , no viruses , no malware . If you find one of this , please come back with a comment to fix this problem in the next version ! Just 381Mb installer path ! Fully protected against slowhack methods ! The game comes with a internet server list updated weekly ! A new Game Menu more attractive and beautifully I'll leave here some snapshots : http://imgur.com/a/5Z7Qm
